name: Double Eagle
overview: Nippon Golf Kyoukai Kanshuu - Double Eagle is a 3d golf game that has 8 selectables characters four males and four females and four caddies. There are also 3 play modes : -PGA mode: The player play a tournament -Free mode: The player play alone -Vs mode: The player play against other player.
